2007-05-25  Daniele Sciascia  <daniele.sciascia@lu.unisi.ch>

	* libgst/dict.c: Turn _gst_find_shared_pool_variable into
	_gst_namespace_association_at, add _gst_namespace_at.
	* libgst/dict.h: Declare it.
