	* lib/cint.c: Added John Stanhope (jehu@vt.edu)'s changes for
	Objective-C calling (Thanks John!!!)
	* lib/gstpub.h: Added defineCFunc.
	* lib/save.c: Added John Stanhope (jehu@vt.edu)'s changes for
	Objective-C calling (Thanks John!!!)
